{%- comment -%}
  CUSTOM · Footer
  Cloned + simplified replacement for Dawn's footer (sections/footer.liquid).
  Hybrid section — see .claude/decisions/004-custom-homepage-sections.md:
  reorderable in the theme editor, all content hardcoded here. The ONLY
  editor-editable setting is the logo image. Lives in the footer section
  group, so it renders site-wide.

  Build status: Unit 2 of 5 — legal text + copyright + scoped CSS.
  Next units: logo render (3), payment icons (4), swap into group (5).
{%- endcomment -%}

{{ 'custom-footer.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

